snippet.title: Valheim: Mistlands Animated Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Our heroes are ready for the next part of their adventure. Are you ready to join them in the Mistlands?

Valheim is available with PC Game Pass, or for purchase on the Steam and Humble stores. The Mistlands update is available now.

Valheim is made by developer Iron Gate, published by Coffee Stain Publishing.

This trailer was produced by https://brikk.se/
